    <topic id="topic_wgv_ybb_mjb">
        <title>PDC Calculation</title>
        <body>
            <p>PDC is calculated using the following equation:</p>
            <p><foreign outputclass="embed-latex"> \begin{align} PPC &amp;= \frac{correct}{(correct
                    + incorrect)} \times 100 \\ &amp;= \frac{correct}{(correct + deletions +
                    substitutions + epenthesis)} \times 100 \end{align}</foreign></p>
        </body>
